        "action": "Ban AI advertisements",
        "additional_details": "We believe Generative AI ads can be dangerous - especially to those who struggle to tell if something\u2019s real or not.\r\n \r\nReal photos, videos and testimonials of products should be used instead.\r\n",
        "background": "The government should create legislation to prevent businesses using generative AI for advertisements, including medical advertisements.",
